## 2. ACTIVE

### Nmap
(-oX for XML, -oN for Nmap, -oG for greppable, or -oA for all three)
nmap -sC -sV target
nmap -p- 127.0.0.1

nmap -sC -sV [target] -oA nameofoutput
nmap -p- [target] -oA allportscan

nmap -p 8025 -sV
---

### Amass — konfiguracja

Wyświetlenia listy wszystkich źródeł danych (data sources), z których Amass może korzystać podczas enumeracji.
amass enum -list

sudo curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OWASP/Amass/master/examples/config.ini > ~/.config/amass/config.ini
ls ~/.config/amass/


 Simply visit https://censys.io/register and register for a free account for process of adding API Keys.

---

### OWASP Amass Project — rekonesans pasywny lub aktywny / narzędzie do rekonesansu domen i infrastruktury internetowej
Zbiera dane z: DNS, certyfikatów SSL, wyszukiwarek, baz pasywnego DNS, API OSINT, brute force słownikowego, WHOIS, ASN


amass enum -active -d microsoft.com | grep api

amass intel -addr [IP]

amass intel -d [domain] -whois

amass enum -passive -d [domain]

amass enum -active -d [domain]

amass enum -active -brute -w /usr/share/wordlists/API_superlist -d [domain] -dir [outputdir]


---

### Gobuster — brute katalogów
gobuster dir -u target.com:8000 -w /home/hapihacker/api/wordlists/common_apis_160
gobuster dir -u target.com:8000/community -w /home/hapihacker/api/wordlists/common_apis_160

gobuster dir -u http://127.0.0.1:8888 -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/d
irectory-list-2.3-medium.txt


---

## DevTools — szybki recon API (crapi /shop)

**Kroki**
F12 → Network → URL column ON -> refresh


**Filtrowanie**
API
v1
graphql



**Export do Postman**
Copy as cURL → Postman → Plik -> Import → Raw text


---

### Kiterunner — discovery endpointów
kr scan http://127.0.0.1 -w ~/api/wordlists/data/kiterunner/routes-large.kite

kr brute <target> -w ~/api/wordlists/data/automated/wordlist.txt


---

### Kiterunner — replay request
kr kb replay "REQUEST" -w ~/api/wordlists/data/kiterunner/routes-large.kite


---

### Format listy targetów
test.com
test.com:443
http://test.com
http://test.com:8888
http://test.com/api



---

